{{Infobox battle item |name = Masterball |image = [[File:Masterball.png]] |caption = In-Game image of the ''Masterball''. |price = {{pdollar}}1,000,000 |location = Fuchsia City, Cianwood City, Fortree City, Pastoria City, Veilstone City, LilyCove City, Poké Mart }}
The '''Masterball''' is a type of pokeball. It automatically tries to catch a wild Pokémon after defeating it if and is the highest type of pokeball avaliable.
==Details== ===Description=== The Ultimate pokeball to capture Pokémon with. It has an 100% catch rate. Each time it is purchased it is 35% more expensive, capping at 100 times the base price
